  "body": "What the title says, if it appends the `\\uFEFF` to fix whitespace it can end up leaving an empty TextNode behind. This is very bad because it offsets the index of children. Also, `renderComponent` still uses `firstChild` which causes it to see the TextNode and replace the content rather than update it as it should.\n\n@zpao We definitely want to merge this sooner rather than later.\n",
